* USE 'aui-node'    :

Get an element:
    A.one('.elementClass');      
    or: 
    A.one('#myElement');

    
Get multiple elements:
    A.all('.box');
    

Add content ot element:
    A.one('.box').html('<p> ... </p>');


Append content to element:
    Y.one('.box p').placeAfter('<p> ... </p>');

Clear element:
    Y.one('#box').empty();












